601
00:40:53,250 --> 00:40:55,309
lt's a miracle.

602
00:40:56,687 --> 00:41:00,248
This is a simple game.

603
00:41:01,125 --> 00:41:03,559
You throw the ball.

604
00:41:03,627 --> 00:41:05,390
You hit the ball.

605
00:41:06,764 --> 00:41:08,732
You catch the ball.

606
00:41:08,799 --> 00:41:10,596
You got it!

607
00:41:12,002 --> 00:41:15,199
We have got a 12-day road trip...

608
00:41:15,272 --> 00:41:18,264
