they're wearing a "dress."

652
00:44:11,715 --> 00:44:13,945
Damn, l hate people
that get the words wrong.

653
00:44:16,820 --> 00:44:18,447
How come you don't like me?

654
00:44:18,522 --> 00:44:21,582
