which is your problem.

655
00:44:23,627 --> 00:44:26,425
But you don't respect the game,
and that's my problem.

656
00:44:26,497 --> 00:44:29,398
- You got a gift.
- What do l got?

657
00:44:29,466 --> 00:44:31,934
You got a gift. When you were
a baby, the gods reached down...

658
00:44:32,002 --> 00:44:34,197
and turned your right arm
into a thunderbolt.

659
00:44:34,271 --> 00:44:37,001
