You were?

669
00:45:01,065 --> 00:45:03,090
You've been in the Show?

670
00:45:03,167 --> 00:45:05,101
Yeah, l was in the Show.

671
00:45:06,203 --> 00:45:10,230
l was in the Show
for 21 days once.

672
00:45:11,875 --> 00:45:14,070
Twenty-one greatest days
of my life.

673
00:45:15,012 --> 00:45:17,242
You never handle your luggage
in the Show.

674
00:45:17,314 --> 00:45:19,009
Somebody else
carries your bags.

675
00:45:19,083 --> 00:45:20,948
lt's great.

676
00:45:21,018 --> 00:45:23,578
You hit white balls
for batting practice.

677
00:45:24,822 --> 00:45:27,814
Ballparks are like cathedrals.

678
00:45:29,460 --> 00:45:31,621
The hotels
all have room service.

679
00:45:33,363 --> 00:45:35,957
The women all have
long legs and brains.

680
00:45:39,336 --> 00:45:40,598
