to get the first out of the inning.

694
00:47:26,343 --> 00:47:29,005
The Bulls will attempt to end
a six-game losing streak...

695
00:47:29,079 --> 00:47:32,139
against the Greensboro Hornets
with Nuke LaLoosh on the hill.

696
00:47:42,726 --> 00:47:44,921
Base hit to center field
off LaLoosh.

697
00:47:51,535 --> 00:47:53,662
That closes the book
on LaLoosh today.

698
00:47:53,737 --> 00:47:56,297
Five earned runs,
five hits, five strikeouts...

699
00:47:56,373 --> 00:47:58,671
five walks
and five wild pitches.

700
00:47:58,742 --> 00:48:01,040
lt's time to tell it
like it is, sports fans.

701
00:48:01,111 --> 00:48:04,342
This is the most wretched
road trip l've seen in 20 years.

702
00:48:04,414 --> 00:48:07,508
And possibly the worst Durham team
in half a century.

703
00:48:07,584 --> 00:48:10,712
ls the modern-day athlete a pale
imitation of the great warriors?

704
00:48:10,787 --> 00:48:12,778
Only Crash Davis
stands out this year.

705
00:48:12,856 --> 00:48:15,222
Begging the question, what are
these boys thinking about?

706
00:48:15,292 --> 00:48:17,055
'Cause it sure ain't baseball.

707
00:48:35,412 --> 00:48:38,438
