check out this.

708
00:48:38,515 --> 00:48:41,780
lce-skaters.
God, look at 'em.

709
00:48:41,852 --> 00:48:44,150
Hey, fellas,
that's what we need, man.

710
00:48:44,221 --> 00:48:46,781
One night with these skaters,
we can get right back on track.

711
00:48:46,857 --> 00:48:47,789
Yeah, right.

712
00:48:47,858 --> 00:48:50,418
Just need a night off
to end our losing streak.

713
00:48:50,494 --> 00:48:52,621
What we need is a rain-out.

714
00:48:52,696 --> 00:48:54,391
l can get us a rain-out.

715
00:48:54,464 --> 00:48:56,898
There ain't been a cloud
in the sky in weeks.

716
00:48:58,702 --> 00:49:01,296
Hundred bucks says l can get us
a rain-out for tomorrow.

717
00:49:08,078 --> 00:49:09,909
You're on.

718
00:49:16,820 --> 00:49:19,448
l ain't paying for this.
Crash, pay for this.

719
00:49:19,523 --> 00:49:21,821
Shut up. You're gonna
wake everybody up.

720
00:49:21,892 --> 00:49:23,951
Let the bonus baby
pay for it.

721
00:49:26,463 --> 00:49:27,987
Jesus, man.

722
00:49:46,316 --> 00:49:48,375
