740
00:53:07,484 --> 00:53:09,042
God, l'm tired.

741
00:53:10,387 --> 00:53:11,718
What a trip.

742
00:53:12,856 --> 00:53:16,257
l was lousy.
l was worse than lousy.

743
00:53:16,326 --> 00:53:20,888
But every time l pitched, it was
like throwing gasoline on a fire.

744
00:53:25,702 --> 00:53:26,634
l mean--

745
00:53:26,703 --> 00:53:29,866
What is all this l, l, l?
What about me?

746
00:53:29,940 --> 00:53:31,931
Aren't you glad to see me?

747
00:53:32,008 --> 00:53:34,067
Don't l look nice?

748
00:53:35,245 --> 00:53:37,577
You look great.
l'm sorry.

749
00:53:37,647 --> 00:53:40,013
l'm just totally exhausted.

750
00:53:40,083 --> 00:53:43,348
Good. Physical exhaustion
can be spiritually fabulous.

751
00:53:43,420 --> 00:53:46,753
What you need
is a good game of catch.

752
00:53:46,823 --> 00:53:47,915
Catch?

